{
  "texts": [
    "Daily price data on NASDAQ 100 companies was extracted from a Kaggle data set foot_6.",
    "Each data represents the percentage change of the closing price from the day before.",
    "Each case is a series of 60 days data.",
    "The target class is defined as 0 if the price did not increase after company report release by more than five percent or 1 else-wise.",
    "PhoneHeartbeatSound and Tools are audio datasets."
  ]
}